🍎 MAC User

```console
# clone
git clone https://github.com/powerline/fonts.git --depth=1

# install
cd fonts

./install.sh

# clean-up a bit
cd ..

rm -rf fonts
```

Open iTerm2->Preferences->Profiles->Change Font-> Meslo LG S DZ Regular for Powerline

